#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/chebyshev.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.chebyshev.chebmul:35
msgid ""
"In general, the (polynomial) product of two C-series results in terms that "
"are not in the Chebyshev polynomial basis set.  Thus, to express the product "
"as a C-series, it is typically necessary to \"reproject\" the product onto "
"said basis set, which typically produces \"unintuitive live\" (but correct) "
"results; see Examples section below."
msgstr ""

